---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import TransformCTA from '../../components/TransformCTA.astro'
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Membresía BHRT — Ella - Renasci Medical Spa"
  description="Soporte continuo para BHRT en mujeres: mensajes, visitas y ajustes de dosis bajo guía médica."
>
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-32 bg-black text-white text-center">
    <div class="px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-0 md:mt-4">
      <div class="inline-block bg-[#F3A2A7]/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border border-[#F3A2A7]/30">Bioidentical Hormone Therapy (BHRT)</div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white mb-4">Membresía BHRT — Ella</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">Acompañamiento continuo, mensajería y visitas para afinar la terapia hormonal de forma segura y efectiva.</p>
      <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-6 inline-block border border-white/20">
        <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-1">Membresía</div>
        <div class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#F3A2A7]">$149/mes</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mt-1">Continuo</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="#details" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-all duración-300 hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-[2px] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#F3A2A7]/50">Ver Detalles<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path></svg></a>
        <a href="tel:+13856092840" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-[#AABFA8] text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-all duración-300 hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-[2px] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#AABFA8]/50" aria-label="Llamar a Renasci"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>385 609 2840</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="bg-background py-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-[#F3A2A7] transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-[#F3A2A7] transition-colors">Servicios</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Membresía BHRT — Ella</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="h-[2px] w-full bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div>

  <section id="details" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-stretch">
        <div class="relative group bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden h-full min-h-[420px] lg:min-h-[520px]">
          <img src="/img/services/Hormone-her.jpg" alt="Membresía BHRT — Ella" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="min-h-[420px] lg:min-h-[520px] flex">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-purple-50 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 h-full flex-1">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#F3A2A7] mb-6">Membresía BHRT — Ella</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p class="mb-4">Soporte continuo diseñado para la terapia hormonal femenina, con mensajería y visitas para ajustar el tratamiento.</p>
              <p class="mb-4">Los ajustes de dosis y el monitoreo mantienen resultados seguros y efectivos conforme evolucionan las necesidades.</p>
              <p>Acceso claro a tu equipo de atención cuando surjan preguntas.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white text-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div><span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg></span><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div></div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#F3A2A7] mb-4">Beneficios</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Por qué la membresía mejora la BHRT para ellas</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Atención Personalizada</h3><p class="text-gray-700">Guía a medida según tus necesidades.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Soporte de Síntomas</h3><p class="text-gray-700">Mensajería y visitas oportunas.</p></div>
        <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Seguridad</h3><p class="text-gray-700">Ajustes monitorizados.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div><span class="mx-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 21a9 9 0 1 0 0-18 9 9 0 0 0 0 18z" /></svg></span><div class="flex-1 h-[2px] bg-[#F3A2A7]"></div></div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#F3A2A7] mb-4">Proceso</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Mensajería, visitas, revisión y ajustes</p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F3A2A7] via-pink-400 to-purple-500 rounded-full opacity-30 hidden lg:block"></div>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8"><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#F3A2A7] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">1</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Mensajería</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Acceso para preguntas y actualizaciones.</p></div></div><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><img src="/images/med-spa-room.jpg" alt="Mensajería" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8"><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#F3A2A7] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">2</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Visitas</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Revisiones periódicas de resultados.</p></div></div><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><img src="/images/inyeccion-botox.jpg" alt="Visitas" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8"><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#F3A2A7] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">3</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Revisión</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Resultados y laboratorios guían cambios.</p></div></div><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><img src="/images/inyeccion-botox.jpg" alt="Revisión" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8"><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-8"><div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white"><div class="flex items-center mb-4"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#F3A2A7] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">4</div><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-gray-900">Ajustes</h3></div><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Actualización de dosis y rutas según necesidad.</p></div></div><div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8"><img src="/images/med-spa-room.jpg" alt="Ajustes" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-2xl" loading="lazy" /></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white text-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-[#F3A2A7] mb-4">Preguntas Frecuentes</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Dudas comunes sobre la membresía BHRT para ella</p>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-3">¿Qué incluye?</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Mensajería, visitas y ajustes.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-3">¿Puedo cancelar en cualquier momento?</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Opciones de membresía flexibles.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-[#F3A2A7] bg-white text-gray-900 hover:ring-2 hover:ring-[#F3A2A7]/60"><h3 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-3">¿Con qué frecuencia?</h3><p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Cadencia adaptada a tu plan.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TransformCTA />
</BaseLayout>
